{"tid":2517321,"cid":37,"subCid":0,"title":"石籬入屋企圖強姦案　鐵閘鎖疑可一匙多開　街坊：唔係幾安全","createTime":"2021-05-05T08:53:54.000Z","updateTime":"2021-05-05T09:07:23.000Z","uid":271829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"82cf6b98142af9ceceb3d40e98d4cce21cc81d3b","tid":2517321,"uid":271829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T08:53:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/dkiG_88_fzNrKbvxz35ZFKyWXAw=/802x451/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/33QBE2G6QRAKXLNGET2DFXZCWU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FdkiG_88_fzNrKbvxz35ZFKyWXAw%3D%2F802x451%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F33QBE2G6QRAKXLNGET2DFXZCWU.jpg&h=73681421&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/S7OMf3Wxh_nctx7SiIc7400u2aA=/802x451/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/ISH6NR7PIZAXNISQPFBHDJYL2E.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FS7OMf3Wxh_nctx7SiIc7400u2aA%3D%2F802x451%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FISH6NR7PIZAXNISQPFBHDJYL2E.JPG&h=a81a371c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n大部分單位外的鐵閘鎖都屬同款由房署安裝的鐵閘鎖。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/m_KsOVGo_NvOYP3ObmuUP5cXHwM=/802x451/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/2GDY2FXMO5HXHOJTLQHI6IENOE.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Fm_KsOVGo_NvOYP3ObmuUP5cXHwM%3D%2F802x451%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F2GDY2FXMO5HXHOJTLQHI6IENOE.JPG&h=1a9a8b23&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n獨居長者王先生認為周一的劫案匪夷所思，並指鐵閘鎖「唔係幾安全」，曾聽聞邨內發生過類似事件，有人用鎖匙進入另一住戶家中爆竊。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/DrD7pAzlJ9XzDXORcNDbVkT0ApE=/802x451/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/4WKLIJ2V5ZFGXDYPLERQLLPTAQ.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FDrD7pAzlJ9XzDXORcNDbVkT0ApE%3D%2F802x451%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F4WKLIJ2V5ZFGXDYPLERQLLPTAQ.JPG&h=0de7e386&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n獨居長者黎女士不擔心有人會入屋爆竊，「唔驚，老人家有咩俾人偷？冇嘢俾人偷。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/__C44pt-FnnkVNFJ6fKRkBFpr8E=/802x451/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/NPA44TGBNNH37BE3GXYDD7TRVE.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F__C44pt-FnnkVNFJ6fKRkBFpr8E%3D%2F802x451%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FNPA44TGBNNH37BE3GXYDD7TRVE.JPG&h=45a39147&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n居於石籬邨十多年的華女士透露可要求房屋署進行更換，「唔洗錢㗎，一毫子都唔洗畀。」<br />\n<br />\n...<br />\n葵涌石籬二邨石禧樓一名男住客，周一（3日）凌晨闖入同幢一名獨居女子家中，不但掠奪財物，更企圖強姦她。女子冷靜應對，更成功聯絡男友人趕到支援，作案男子事敗後，被警方於同日拘捕。據悉，疑犯是女事主的同層鄰居，他身上的鎖匙可打開部份同層單位的原裝鐵閘鎖，與以往天水圍某公屋戶投訴過的「一匙開多戶」事件同出一轍。《蘋果》正就事件向房屋署查詢。<br />\n...<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/breaking/20210505/4TI5YHNCYFCNJDKXAOY3UUKHDA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20210505%2F4TI5YHNCYFCNJDKXAOY3UUKHDA%2F&d=d89kjzbMxLru5B8Znw6mnwRqNnYsekRkiG%2Fa4%2F0EtZc%3D&h=5c13924b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20210505%2F4TI5YHNCYFCNJDKXAOY3UUKHDA%2F&h=9fb116d0\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/breaking/20210505/4TI5YHNCYFCNJDKXAOY3UUKHDA/</a>"},{"pid":"5885ad9b12c49c477e3fd9f524169fde66a65d72","tid":2517321,"uid":341649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T08:57:16.000Z","msg":"唔洗錢㗎，一毫子都唔洗畀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"30de4132bd3371ecf4a79a9b50595c6622cdc66c","tid":2517321,"uid":60412,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T09:00:25.000Z","msg":"cls ,一條匙開晒"},{"pid":"74dbb31d557db8422105da33fce33ef9baaa826f","tid":2517321,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T09:02:28.000Z","msg":"N年前城市追擊都做過既TOPIC"},{"pid":"051c7d7e0878265ead0a803cc5c80dd36c7623d5","tid":2517321,"uid":164896,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T09:07:23.000Z","msg":"鐵閘根本唔安全,真正防盜係木門和木門鎖,但若遇到專業開鎖佬,乜門乜鎖都無用."}]}